results.name: cq-social-livefyre-pkg
results.description: Livefyre provides industry leading aggregation and curation capabilities, allowing you to publish valuable user generated content from social networks to your site in minutes. Instantly build and customize dynamic and engaging experiences using a suite of Social Components including Maps, Galleries, and Media Walls. Livefyre Social Depth Applications offer best-in-class filtering and moderation technology, allowing you to easily discover, organize, obtain rights, and utilize the most impactful UGC. With this offering brands can marry content sourced from Adobe Creative Cloud with social content discovered and curated by Livefyre, and then easily deliver these experiences in Adobe Experience Manager. Enterprises that can curate and deploy user generated content in combination with brand-created content effectively will create more authentic and compelling experiences on owned and third-party properties. To learn more about how Livefyre and Adobe come together, contact Livefyre.
